          <td width="138" valign="top" height="75"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Research 
            Interests:</b></font></td>
          <td width="388" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Arial">Research interests include the biosynthesis and catabolism of abscisic acid, the abscisic acid-carotenoid interrelationship in vivo and plant responses to stress (particularly to ABA at the cell level). At present concentrating on the cell-free metabolism of abscisic acid. Also involved in collaborative research with industry looking at carotenoid accumulation and pigmentation, and fruit development of tropical and sub-tropical species (particularly citrus and avocado), and the biotechnological production of natural �-carotene (Dunaliella).</font></td>
        </tr>
